column5: Hello,Can anyone tell me how the water levels are doing this year compared to last years by Flin Flon, Manitoba? I am curious to see if we will be able to get to camp this year or if the water is up maybe our road is washed out.Thanks,rngrfshm
Not much snow in northern Manitoba this year and what we have is melting,i think its going to be a dry year with lower lake levels unless we get alot of snow or rain this fall.
